    xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
    xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xl="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
    xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
    xmlns:svg="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:mth="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"
    xmlns:db="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
    xml:id="create_data_element_group_set">
    <title>Create or edit a data element group set</title>
    <?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20160513T112352+0200" comment="At next revision, rephrase into active voice." flag="done"?>
    <para>Data element group sets allows you to categorise multiple data element groups into a set.
        The system uses data element group sets during analysis and reporting to combine similar
        data element groups into a common theme.</para>
    <?oxy_comment_end?>
    <orderedlist>
        <listitem>
            <para>Open the <emphasis role="bold">Maintenance</emphasis> app and click <emphasis
                    role="bold">Data elements</emphasis> > <emphasis role="bold">Data element group
                    set</emphasis>.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Click the add
                <?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20160510T112410+0200" comment="Do not refer to the FAB as an icon, according to MS Manual of Style." flag="done"?>button<?oxy_comment_end?>.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Fill in the form:</para>
            <orderedlist>
                <listitem>
                    <para><emphasis role="bold">Name</emphasis></para>
                </listitem>
                <listitem>
                    <para><emphasis role="bold">Code</emphasis></para>
                </listitem>
                <listitem>
                    <para><emphasis role="bold">Description</emphasis></para>
                </listitem>
                <listitem>
                    <para><emphasis role="bold">Compulsory</emphasis></para>
                </listitem>
                <listitem>
                    <para><emphasis role="bold">Data dimension</emphasis></para>
                </listitem>
            </orderedlist>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Select data element groups and assign them.</para>
            <?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20160513T113037+0200" comment="At next revision, review this para. Is it necessary? Does it add value?" flag="done"?>
            <para>Available data element groups are displayed in the left panel. Data element groups
                that are currently members of the data element group set are displayed in the right
                hand panel.</para>
            <?oxy_comment_end?>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Click <emphasis role="bold">Save</emphasis>.</para>
        </listitem>
    </orderedlist>
</section>
